{"tid":540154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府開設「領土主權展示館」　展示釣魚島等資料","createTime":"2018-01-25T08:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T10:28:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5e1e363418062a0eedc9c5a071ceac33cfadf1","tid":540154,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1377193_1_L_20180125131504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1377193_1_L_20180125131504.jpg&h=06f06e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本政府在東京日比谷公園的市政會館開設「領土主權展示館」，展示尖閣諸島，即支那所稱的釣魚島，以及竹島，即南韓稱為獨島的相關資料，目的是作為常設設施，宣傳這些島嶼是「日本的固有領土」。<br />\n<br />\n領土問題擔當相江崎鐵磨在開館儀式上表示，這間展示館是宣傳日本領土主權的關鍵設施。<br />\n<br />\n支那一直強調，釣魚島及附屬島嶼是支那的固有領土。"},{"pid":"c438f48556fef7f054eccef51d4308f79ebe7c68","tid":540154,"uid":9348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"係尖閣諸島"},{"pid":"b28bfe761f310234157ac2c4c7d4c1e9e418aad2","tid":540154,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c438f48556fef7f054eccef51d4308f79ebe7c68","tid":540154,"uid":9348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"係尖閣諸島"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"SORRY <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735b4fff386ea3d33a94a83043e6997d460b2daa","tid":540154,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2acc019cfcf60e5070d74745d7e3d1666d09d85","tid":540154,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"支那遊客must go"}]}